{
  "stem": "19596.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 324.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were about a hundred of those 50-gallon drums with soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to be loaded like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I worked some time in cleaning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I-- I-- I orgami-- I organized my-- I want to look around what was-- what there was outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was already a bit better then, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Felt a bit better and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The normal food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A bowl of soup which consisted of tiny, mini pieces of meat, mostly peas or beans, and a thick soup or cabbage.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then you got a quota of a black bread, and you got a tiny little-- a spoon of margarine, like you'd get here for breakfast, you know those things you got in the hotels.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the same in jam.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that is your daily ration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you do very well, you can get maybe a repeat of soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you were wor-- working very well, they give you-- if there's some soup left in the-- in the-- in the thing, they give you another half.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I have been approached by somebody who liked me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I made a connection there with one of the prisoners in the fire brigade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a prominent prisoner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means he was-- he was already in a position-- a very prominent position, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a Christian Pole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Zygmund.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Zygmund Zabolowski, and his number was 88.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he had a very good position there, and he knew all the Poles and all the connections in the kitchen and here and there and there and there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he wanted English lessons.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
